# Standard Commit Message Format

When suggesting commit messages for this project, use this format:

```
feat(vX.Y.Z): brief description

- Bullet point summarizing change 1
- Bullet point summarizing change 2
- Bullet point summarizing change 3
```

**Structure:**
- **Subject:** `feat(version): brief description` — type (feat/fix/chore), version in parens, short summary
- **Body:** Bullet points (one per significant change), concise and scoped

**Example:**
```
feat(v0.3.0): auth M2 OIDC integration

- NextAuth v5 with custom M2 Auth OIDC provider (PKCE + state)
- Route groups: (public) landing page, (app) auth-gated pages
- UserBar component with federated sign-out
- Server-only env validation via Zod (env.server.ts)
- Auth error page with NextAuth error code mapping
```
